  <summary date="2020-04-29T18:28:41Z" status="Introduced in House">Emergency Cannabis Small Business Health and Safety Act

This bill makes a cannabis-related legitimate business or service provider eligible for specified Small Business Administration (SBA) programs established in response to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019), and it exempts the SBA from liability under federal laws or regulations solely for providing a loan or guarantee to such a business or service provider.</summary>
